{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探究影响电荷间相互作用力的因素。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">控制变量法，在带电量相同的情况下探究库仑力的大小与距离的关系；在距离不变的情况下探究库仑力与带电量的关系。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">带正电小球、铁架台、带丝线小球</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">.将带正电小球接触带丝线小球，使带丝线小球带上电；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2.将带正电小球固定在铁架台右侧某位置；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3.将带丝线小球依次悬挂在铁架台上不同位置；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">4.观察丝线偏离竖直方向的角度变化；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">5.保持带丝线小球位置不变，改变带正电小球的带电量，观察丝线偏离竖直方向的角度变化<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电荷之间的作用力随着电荷量的增大而增大，随着距离的增大而减小。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><em><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><em>F=kq</em></span></span></em><sub><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1</span></span></sub><em><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><em>q</em></span></span></em><sub><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></span></sub><em><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><em>/r</em></span></span></em><sup><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></span></sup></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}